!skill
n:ACMS_daily_diary
v:1.0.0
d:TaskArchitecture
sd:DiaryWriter
fq:TaskArchitecture/DiaryWriter/ACMS_daily_diary
m:"Generate a structured daily diary entry for the Obsidian vault from a summary of the day's work."
p:"ACMS Daily Diary Writer — disciplined, concise, architecturally aware."
t:reflective-precise
tl:[file_write,file_read,datetime_now]
